      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<div class=\"contentLayout2\"><style>[data-colorid=eb7ve5lbop]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=eb7ve5lbop]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=qhh8wqygxy]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=qhh8wqygxy]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=vwxsci807x]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=vwxsci807x]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=xcw73ljfi1]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=xcw73ljfi1]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=p0ekyspxmt]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=p0ekyspxmt]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=y3jp1s887m]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=y3jp1s887m]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=w7ov0ywccd]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=w7ov0ywccd]{color:#004eb3}</style>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"shading_learingPath_banner.jpg\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/599163179/shading_learingPath_banner.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1761725542429&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=320\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/599163179/shading_learingPath_banner.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1761725542429&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"714\" data-width=\"1695\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"636059664\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"shading_learingPath_banner.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"599163179\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"33\" data-media-id=\"978b2edc-abe2-461e-9c21-06fbee963cca\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/599163179/shading_learingPath_banner.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1761725542429&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1520&amp;height=640 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/599163179/shading_learingPath_banner.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1761725542429&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=320 1x\" /></span><h1 id=\"PxrSurface-StartHere\"><strong><span data-colorid=\"vwxsci807x\">Start Here</span></strong></h1><p>A good place to start if you&rsquo;re new to mighty PxrSurface, the main shader used here at Pixar Animation Studios.</p><hr /></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout three-equal\" data-layout=\"three-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<a href=\"/wiki/spaces/RU/pages/606928975/PxrSurface+Fundamentals\" data-linked-resource-id=\"606928975\" data-linked-resource-version=\"4\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"fundamentalsThumb.jpg\" width=\"261\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/599163179/fundamentalsThumb.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758209459436&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=261&amp;height=261\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/599163179/fundamentalsThumb.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758209459436&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"500\" data-width=\"500\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"606732319\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"fundamentalsThumb.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"599163179\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"33\" data-media-id=\"3b25b59d-c627-4e64-be42-761dd820502b\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/599163179/fundamentalsThumb.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758209459436&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=500&amp;height=500 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/599163179/fundamentalsThumb.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758209459436&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=261&amp;height=261 1x\" /></span></a><p><strong><span data-colorid=\"xcw73ljfi1\">PxrSurface Fundamentals</span></strong><br />If you&rsquo;re new to PxrSurface, this is a good place to start with our official training.</p></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://rmanwiki-27.pixar.com/space/RU/619773953/Dielectrics+and+Conductors\" rel=\"nofollow\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"Conductors_thumb.jpg\" width=\"261\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/599163179/Conductors_thumb.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1759489080700&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=261&amp;height=261\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/599163179/Conductors_thumb.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1759489080700&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"400\" data-width=\"400\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"619512122\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"Conductors_thumb.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"599163179\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"33\" data-media-id=\"c9531a4e-1ee6-4303-ac3b-cd851b0a0a49\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/599163179/Conductors_thumb.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1759489080700&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=400&amp;height=400 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/599163179/Conductors_thumb.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1759489080700&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=261&amp;height=261 1x\" /></span></a><p><strong><span data-colorid=\"eb7ve5lbop\">Dielectrics &amp; Conductors</span></strong><br />Learn the difference between  Dielectric and Conductive materials.</p></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p /></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<hr /><h1 id=\"PxrSurface-NextSteps\"><strong><span data-colorid=\"w7ov0ywccd\">Next Steps</span></strong></h1><p>Now you&rsquo;ve learnt the basics of the PxrSurface, here are some next steps for you to learn.</p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout three-equal\" data-layout=\"three-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<a href=\"/wiki/spaces/RU/pages/619741326/PxrSurface+-+Metallic+Workflow\" data-linked-resource-id=\"619741326\" data-linked-resource-version=\"3\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"Metallic_thumb.jpg\" width=\"261\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/599163179/Metallic_thumb.jpg?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1759488499405&amp;