tlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/599163179/GlassThumb.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758718043063&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"500\" data-width=\"500\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"612172050\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"GlassThumb.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"599163179\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"33\" data-media-id=\"f33bff6a-7f4c-42c2-bc33-9cdd79d31bc4\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/599163179/GlassThumb.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758718043063&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=500&amp;height=500 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/599163179/GlassThumb.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758718043063&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=261&amp;height=261 1x\" /></span></a><p><strong><span data-colorid=\"p0ekyspxmt\">PxrSurface Glass</span></strong><br />Learn how to make beautiful colored glass.</p></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<a href=\"/wiki/spaces/RU/pages/619806721/PxrSurface+-+Material+Layering\" data-linked-resource-id=\"619806721\" data-linked-resource-version=\"7\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"layering_thumb.jpg\" width=\"261\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/599163179/layering_thumb.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1759490806882&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=261&amp;height=261\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/599163179/layering_thumb.jpg?version=1&amp;